params._addresses: Array of [govAddress, zorroControllerAddress, ZORROAddress, wantAddress, token0Address, earnedAddress, farmContractAddress, rewardsAddress, poolAddress, uniRouterAddress, zorroLPPool, zorroLPPoolToken0, zorroLPPoolToken1]
params._balancerPoolWeights: Weights of assets in Balancer pools. Array of [balancerPoolUSDCWeightBasisPoints, balancerPoolWantWeightBasisPoints, balancerPoolEarnWeightBasisPoints, balancerPoolToken0WeightBasisPoints]
params._balancerPools: Addresses of Balancer pools for performing swaps. Array of [balancerPoolUSDCToWant, balancerPoolUSDCToToken0]
params._isCOREStaking: If true, is for staking just core token of AMM (e.g. CAKE for Pancakeswap, BANANA for Apeswap, etc.). Set to false for Zorro single staking vault
params._isHomeChain: Whether this contract is deployed on the home chain (BSC)
params._isZorroComp: This vault is for compounding. If true, will trigger farming/unfarming on earn events. Set to false for Zorro single staking vault
params._pid: Pool ID this Vault is associated with
params._swapPathStartIndexes: An array of start indexes within _swapPaths to represent the start of a new swap path
params._swapPaths: A flattened array of swap paths for a Uniswap style router. Ordered as: [earnedToZORROPath, earnedToToken0Path, earnedToToken1Path, USDCToToken0Path, USDCToToken1Path, earnedToZORLPPoolToken0Path, earnedToZORLPPoolToken1Path, earnedToUSDCPath, USDCToZORROPath]

params._account: address of user that this deposit is intended for
params._wantAmt: amount of Want token to deposit/stake

params._amountUSDC: The USDC quantity to exchange (must already be deposited)

params._amount: The Want token quantity to exchange (must be deposited beforehand)
params._maxMarketMovementAllowed: The max slippage allowed for swaps. 1000 = 0 %, 995 = 0.5%, etc.

params._amount: The amount of the tokens to transfer
params._to: The address to transfer tokens to
params._token: Address of the ERC20 token to transfer

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._entranceFeeFactor: Entrance fee numerator (higher means smaller percentage)
params._withdrawFeeFactor: Withdrawal fee numerator (higher means smaller percentage)

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._account: The address of the owner of vault investment
params._harvestOnly: If true, will only harvest Zorro tokens but not do a withdrawal
